demonstrate 
thoroughness to the 
user.\nIt also helps 
the user understand 
the progress of the 
task and overall 
progress of their 
requests.\n\n## When 
to Use This Tool\nUse 
this tool proactively 
in these 
scenarios:\n\n1. 
Complex multistep 
tasks - When a task 
requires 3 or more 
distinct steps or 
actions\n2. 
Non-trivial and 
complex tasks - Tasks 
